Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 20-11-2024

JUST Medical Center Automation is committed to protecting your privacy. This privacy policy outlines how your information is collected, used, and protected when using our app. By using the app, you agree to the practices described in this policy.

Information We Collect
We collect the following types of information to provide and improve our services:

Personal Information:

Name, email address, phone number, and other details provided during registration.
Additional information submitted after the first login (e.g., student ID, department, etc.).
Usage Information:

Information about how you use the app, including interactions with features such as the dashboard, doctor profiles, and prescriptions.
Device Information:

Device type, operating system, and app version.
Location Information:

If you use the call ambulance feature, the app may access your location to enhance emergency assistance.
How We Use Your Information
We use the collected information for the following purposes:

To facilitate login, registration, and email OTP verification.
To display personalized dashboards and medical profiles.
To enable features such as viewing doctors, prescriptions, and editing user profiles.
To ensure the security of your account through password management.
To improve app functionality and user experience.
How We Protect Your Information
We take the security of your information seriously and implement industry-standard measures to safeguard it. These include:

Encryption of sensitive data.
Secure access controls to prevent unauthorized access.
Regular app updates to address potential vulnerabilities.
Third-Party Services
We may use trusted third-party services to enhance functionality (e.g., email verification services). These services are required to comply with data protection standards.

Your Rights
As a user, you have the following rights:

Access and update your personal information through the app's profile editing features.
Request the deletion of your account by contacting support.
Opt out of non-essential data collection.
Data Retention
We retain your data only as long as necessary to provide the app's services and comply with legal requirements.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be communicated via the app or our official website.

Contact Us
